Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:16.00,Main,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:17.39,Main,,0,0,0,,我們動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:22.32,Main,,0,0,0,,吾名惠比壽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:25.92,Main,,0,0,0,,獲持諱名 止於此面
